    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The literature survey provides a robust evidence base demonstrating that the CFD hemolysis model produces predictions consistent with published experimental findings across comparable pump geometries. The assessment team concludes that the model is sufficiently credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
